videos.description: TCU's Alex Robinson gets a steal and then feeds Vladimir Brodziansky for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: TCU turns a steal into a two-handed dunk

videos.description: Kansas' Frank Mason III finds Josh Jackson on an alley-oop off an inbounds pass and Jackson throws down the slam.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson finishes a vicious dunk off an inbounds pass

videos.description: Kansas's Frank Mason III feeds Landen Lucas with an alley-oop pass and Lucas delivers with the dunk.
videos.headline: Landen Lucas throws down an alley-oop dunk

videos.description: TCU's Desmond Bane rejects Kansas' Lagerald Vick with a block on a fast break
videos.headline: TCU's Bane protects the rim with a powerful block

videos.description: TCU's Vladimir Brodziansky gets a block and follows it up with a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Brodziansky gets a block on one end and a dunk on the other

videos.description: TCU's Alex Robinson picks off a Kansas pass and gets a layup at the other end.
videos.headline: TCU forces a steal and cuts the Kansas lead to 4

videos.description: Postgame Breakdown of Kansas' 86-80 victory over TCU
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown of Kansas' 86-80 victory over TCU
